        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-howto-template-gallery"
        },
        "markdown": "## Planned Scope\n\nThis guide should eventually teach:\n- how to browse the template gallery\n- how to choose the smallest useful template\n- how to adapt the declaration, surfaces, and starter nodes without losing the template's shape\n\nFor now, use the gallery itself as the source of truth."
